paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the association between genetically determined blood pressure, antihypertensive drug classes, and frailty, with a focus on the KCNH2 gene as a target for beta-blockers. However, no specific genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene are mentioned.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant data for the KCNH2 gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper mentions KCNH2 as a target gene but does not report any specific variants or penetrance data related to it.
